Best regards,
[Your Name]
[Your Business Name]
[Contact Details]`,
        smsBody: "Hi [Client Name], following up on the quote for your event on [Date]. Any questions or ready to book? Let me know! - [Your Name]",
        isDefault: false,
        isAutoRespond: false
      },
      {
